@footnote{@code{ORO} stands for @dfn{Orography} in the NCAR climate model.
@math{@var{ORO} < .5} selects the gridpoints which are covered by ocean.}:
@example
ncwa -m ORO -M .5 -o lt -w gw -a lat,lon in.nc out.nc
